心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n哈 我都同你一樣 我都唔中意死讀書 一定要識原理<br />\n做control 做lab 玩電腦program成日俾人話學得好快 係咪痴線<br />\n又係唔中意考試 分數永遠游走6-70<br />\n到走到research果步 完全係我天下 個感覺好興奮<br />\n你都唔好放棄自己 係香港要讀大學只係時間問題<br />\n總會係有你既地方"},{"pid":"38e2d27b10478879b8ae9332a7887038855f7e0d","tid":236211,"uid":18704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T05:02:51.000Z","msg":"巴打頂住<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我自問自己讀書都唔勁 今年ass hole都捱緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  你唔係自己一個捱緊嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b67d2fee4e52cc807f875f1b68789be9b7a729fc","tid":236211,"uid":99243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T05:15:15.000Z","msg":"想脫貧都有好多方法既，唔一定要讀書<br />\n關鍵在於將努力放係應放既地方"},{"pid":"7ebb3e7ed8b49c5703f3f4256648e604ad136966","tid":236211,"uid":44547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T06:03:43.000Z","msg":"你牙蘇仔讀唔讀都冇分別架啦。 去做野好過啦"},{"pid":"1e5d08c169e6fa68d022cba969c49da56b2a84a5","tid":236211,"uid":22136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T06:23:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔讀書嗰人就冇用，不如早日投胎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都好想再刷首抽 去個小康之家都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n死又唔敢死 每日都唔知自己做緊咩<br />\n有冇人記得我<br />\n有冇人明白我</blockquote><br />\n係你個係未開竅啫 未有負擔</blockquote><br />\n但家庭負擔已經好重 全家冇人讀到asso<br />\n我讀到佢地對我期望更加高 想我入大學<br />\n想我做文職<br />\n對於我屋企做到文職已經好叻<br />\n其實壓力好大負擔好重 點解仲柒下柒下咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf139fa40c2f4abd8c855f1f854e24bd66de7c34","tid":236211,"uid":22136,"like":0